X_i \sim N(\mu_i, \sigma_i) \text{ and } i=1, \dots, n\,
\sum_{i=1}^n a_i X_i \sim N\left(\sum_{i=1}^n a_i \mu_i, \sum_{i=1}^n (a_i \sigma_i)^2 \right).
